@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

top to bottom direction
title FIG-10-03. Horizon Bank Payment EventStorming Board

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 45

rectangle "Retail Customer\n<<Actor>>" as Customer #FFFFFF
rectangle "Horizon Digital\nChannels\n<<System>>" as Channels #F2F5F7
rectangle "Payments Platform\n<<System>>" as Payments #F2F5F7
rectangle "Financial Crime\nPlatform\n<<System>>" as FinCrime #F2F5F7
rectangle "Core Deposit\nSystem\n<<System>>" as Core #F2F5F7
rectangle "Operations Analyst\n<<Actor>>" as Ops #FFFFFF
rectangle "Fraud Investigator\n<<Actor>>" as Fraud #FFFFFF

rectangle "SubmitPayment\nInstruction\n<<Command>>" as Submit #DDEEFF
rectangle "PaymentInstruction\nReceived\n<<Event>>" as Received #FFE0B2
rectangle "ValidatePayment\nInstruction\n<<Command>>" as Validate #DDEEFF
rectangle "PaymentInstruction\nValidated\n<<Event>>" as Validated #FFE0B2
rectangle "PaymentInstruction\nRejected\n<<Event>>" as ValidationRejected #FFE0B2
rectangle "RequestPayment\nScreening\n<<Command>>" as RequestScreening #DDEEFF
rectangle "PaymentScreening\nCompleted\n<<Event>>" as ScreeningCompleted #FFE0B2
rectangle "Payment routing\npolicy\n<<Policy>>" as RoutingPolicy #EAF6E8

rectangle "PostPayment\n<<Command>>" as PostPayment #DDEEFF
rectangle "RequestPayment\nRepair\n<<Command>>" as RequestRepair #DDEEFF
rectangle "RejectPayment\n<<Command>>" as RejectPayment #DDEEFF
rectangle "OpenFraudCase\n<<Command>>" as OpenFraud #DDEEFF

rectangle "PaymentPosted\n<<Event>>" as Posted #FFE0B2
rectangle "PaymentRepair\nRequested\n<<Event>>" as RepairRequested #FFE0B2
rectangle "PaymentRejected\n<<Event>>" as PaymentRejected #FFE0B2
rectangle "FraudCase\nOpened\n<<Event>>" as FraudOpened #FFE0B2
rectangle "Open question:\nwho owns repair SLA?\n<<Question>>" as Question #FFF8DC

Customer -down-> Channels : initiates
Channels -down-> Submit
Submit -down-> Received : produces
Received -down-> Validate
Validate -down-> Validated : valid
Validate -right-> ValidationRejected : invalid
Validated -down-> RequestScreening
RequestScreening -down-> ScreeningCompleted : produces
ScreeningCompleted -down-> RoutingPolicy : triggers

RoutingPolicy -down-> PostPayment : route post
RoutingPolicy -left-> RequestRepair : route repair
RoutingPolicy -right-> RejectPayment : route reject
RoutingPolicy -down-> OpenFraud : route fraud case

PostPayment -down-> Posted : produces
RequestRepair -down-> RepairRequested : produces
RejectPayment -down-> PaymentRejected : produces
OpenFraud -down-> FraudOpened : produces

Payments .. Validate : owns validation
FinCrime .. RequestScreening : performs screening
Core .. PostPayment : posts payment
Ops .. RequestRepair : handles repair
Fraud .. OpenFraud : investigates
Question .. RepairRequested

legend bottom
Blue boxes are commands. Orange boxes are events. Green is a policy.
The board is a discovery view, not BPMN and not a runtime deployment view.
endlegend
@enduml
